quotes.quote: ”Never wish life were easier, wish that you were better.” - Jim Rohn
”You Learn More From Failure Than From Success. Don’t Let It Stop You. Failure Builds Character.” – Unknown
”The way to get started is to quit talking and begin doing.” - Walt Disney
”All our dreams can come true, if we have the courage to pursue them.” - Walt Disney
”We May Encounter Many Defeats But We Must Not Be Defeated.” – Maya Angelou
”Live your life, be happy”. - Simone Dalager
”Har de ikke sex foran hans lig?” - Martin M. Svensson
”Fake it till you make it” - Unknown & Mira Berg Schmidt
